tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE financial_behavior_outliers (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    transaction_amount NUMERIC,
    transaction_date DATE,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    transaction_category VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE financial_transactions (
    transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    transaction_amount DECIMAL,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP,
    transaction_type TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE outliers (
    outlier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    outlier_reason TEXT,
    outlier_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE users (
 user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(255),
 email VARCHAR(255),
 age INT
 )

CREATE TABLE transactions (
 transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 user_id INT,
 amount DECIMAL(10,2),
 transaction_date DATE
 )

CREATE TABLE categories (
 category_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 name VARCHAR(255)
 )

CREATE TABLE outliers (
 outlier_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 user_id INT,
 reason VARCHAR(255),
 outlier_flag BOOLEAN
 )

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    transaction_id INT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    transaction_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE accounts (
    account_id INT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    account_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    balance DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    opened_date DATE NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE outliers (
    outlier_id INT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    outlier_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    outlier_date DATE NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);

CREATE TABLE alerts (
    alert_id INT NOT NULL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT NOT NULL,
    alert_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    alert_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);
